        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nthe yaml and rst linters reported errors..\n\nsee the log to see the errors and most of the time the associated fix\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/integration-master-yaml-lint/37/console\n\nit seems you introduced a broken link in the scaleout rst doc\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/integration-master-rst-lint/7/console\n\n22:16:13 (line   12) broken    https://git.onap.org/integration/tree/docs/files/scaleout/dcae_blueprint.yaml - 404 Client Error: Not found for url: https://git.onap.org/integration/tree/docs/files/scaleout/dcae_blueprint.yaml\n\nyou can run all the linters locally on your machine (needs to install tox)\nby running tox-eyaml and tox-erst",
